{"id": 1558, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今，你觉得哪些对女性的称呼其实是有点问题的？", "description": "被称为“小姐”“姑娘”“美女”“女神”，每一种似乎都有点尴尬，这是为啥？（题图来自：Miguel Ángel Camprubí）", "record_count": 6898, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/201703081030286znyboUluIDC8YQ3.png", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-03-08T02:35:13Z", "options": [{"id": 176384, "content": "80岁以上叫大姐，其他的叫妹子", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645296}, {"id": 176640, "content": "对于陌生的人称呼，与其叫美女?帅哥? 不如尊称一声您好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 649741}, {"id": 177152, "content": "男生喜欢被叫叔吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 841962}, {"id": 176897, "content": "叫同学吧\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 941654}, {"id": 176386, "content": "我自己明明长得一般 还非要在公众场合叫女神 你真的很油腻 我也真的很尴尬 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957550}, {"id": 176898, "content": "日报小编说话也要负点责任，排在第一位获得200+赞，做出有歧义的引导还怎么让人信服：古汉语“先生”本就没有性别之分，只是对有德行的长者的尊称，或者是某一类职业的代表，就像现在说“医生\"一样，难道一定要交XX女医生才不算性别歧视么。只是在现代汉语中逐步分化出性别的指向，小编这样引导也不可不谓“伪女权主义”", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 273667}, {"id": 176387, "content": "Mademoiselle~", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 947397}, {"id": 176643, "content": "靓女，不知为什么听着有些不太舒服。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935508}, {"id": 176644, "content": "我的干女儿?", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 933144}, {"id": 180484, "content": "小姐姐", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 818045}, {"id": 176389, "content": "小姑凉。。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 962787}, {"id": 176645, "content": "美女！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 283795},